# travel_a2a generated session outputs -- raw LLM responses, timestamps,
# session IDs, regenerated (and non-deterministic for real Ollama runs) on
# every execution. Keep the scaffolding README.md tracked, ignore only the
# per-run session directories underneath. See reports/travel_a2a/ for the
# content-free, committed summary of what a given run found.
outputs/travel_a2a/attack_smoke/*/
outputs/travel_a2a/mock_sessions/*/
outputs/travel_a2a/step6_mini_validation/*/
outputs/travel_a2a/formal_workload_mock/*/
